Package: somervillema.gov
Title: City of Somerville Open Data (Socrata SODA) Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the City of Somerville Open Data portal
    (data.somervillema.gov). Query 27 Socrata datasets including police CAD,
    crime reports, 311 requests, permits, citations, happiness surveys, and more.
    Includes LLM context injection via somer_context().
